(Processor's primary processing region is the United States. Application hosting \(Vercel\) and database / file) Tj
T* (storage \(Supabase\) operate from US-region infrastructure. There is no EU-region or African-region) Tj
T* (processing option in production today; Controllers requiring a specific regional processing commitment should) Tj
T* (contact privacy@decision-intel.com before contract execution to discuss feasibility.) Tj
ET
