(Where Processing involves transfer of Personal Data from the European Economic Area, the United) Tj
T* (Kingdom, or another jurisdiction whose data-protection law restricts cross-border transfer, the parties rely on) Tj
T* (the Standard Contractual Clauses \(Commission Implementing Decision \(EU\) 2021/914\), the UK International) Tj
T* (Data Transfer Addendum, or the equivalent standard mechanism for the originating jurisdiction \(including,) Tj
T* (where applicable, NDPR cross-border transfer requirements for Nigerian data subjects\). These clauses are) Tj
T* (incorporated by reference. Processor will not transfer Personal Data to any third country whose) Tj
T* (data-protection law would prevent the application of an appropriate transfer mechanism.) Tj
